Immunity|true	FACT:Alchemist_CF_BrewPotion|true	FACT:Alchemist_CF_PoisonResistance|true	FACT:Alchemist_CF_PoisonUse|true	FACT:Alchemist_CF_SwiftPoisoning|true	FACT:Alchemist_CF_PoisonImmunity|true
Winged Marauder				KEY:Alchemist Archetype ~ Winged Marauder		CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.AlchemistArchetype																																		PRECLASS:1,Alchemist=1		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Alchemist Archetype ~ Winged Marauder],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Alchemist_Archetype_ClassSkills=True,Alchemist_Archetype_Mutagen=True,Alchemist_Archetype_PersistentMutagen=True]																																																DESC:Goblin alchemists have created a mixture of pheromones that they use to manipulate and entice giant vultures or dire bats to do their bidding. These goblins strap harnesses to the chests of these flying animals and hang beneath them, dropping flaming alchemical solutions on the helpless folks below.																																																																																																																																																																											ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Winged Marauder ~ Class Skills|PRECLASS:1,Alchemist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Winged Marauder ~ Flying Beast Tamer|PRECLASS:1,Alchemist=1																																																																																																																																																																																					COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.104																																																																																																																																																																																															FACT:Alchemist_Archetype_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Alchemist_Archetype_Mutagen|true	FACT:Alchemist_Archetype_PersistentMutagen|true	FACT:Alchemist_CF_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Alchemist_CF_Mutagen|true	FACT:Alchemist_CF_PersistentMutagen|true
Alchemical Trapper			KEY:Alchemist Archetype ~ Alchemical Trapper	CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.AlchemistArchetype																																		PRECLASS:1,Alchemist=1		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Alchemist Archetype ~ Alchemical Trapper],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Alchemist_Archetype_Discovery2=True,Alchemist_Archetype_Discovery4=True]																																																							DESC:Because kobolds rely on traps to soften up enemies, kobold alchemists learn to turn bombs into traps. When such alchemists are preparing defenses against larger creatures that might enter their tunnels and attempt to exterminate them, their skills mean the difference between life and death.																																																																																																																																																																												ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Alchemical Trapper ~ Bomb Trap|PRECLASS:1,Alchemist=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Alchemical Trapper ~ Trapfinding|PRECLASS:1,Alchemist=4																																																																																																																																																																																					COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.128																																																																																																																																																																																															FACT:Alchemist_Archetype_Discovery2|true	FACT:Alchemist_Archetype_Discovery4|true	FACT:Alchemist_CF_Discovery2|true	FACT:Alchemist_CF_Discovery4|true

