Flying Beast Tamer			KEY:Winged Marauder ~ Flying Beast Tamer		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Alchemist Class Features.WingedMarauderClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.Animal Companion																																																																																																		DEFINE:AnimalCompanionLVL|0	DEFINE:AnimalCompanionMasterLVL|0			DESC:A winged marauder acquires a flying mount as an animal companion. This works as the druid animal companion class feature, except the marauder must select a dire bat (Bestiary p.30) or giant vulture (Bestiary 3 p.312). The marauder's effective druid level is equal to his alchemist level. A marauder and his companion don't gain the share spells ability.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										BONUS:VAR|AnimalCompanionMasterLVL|AlchemistLVL																					FOLLOWERS:Animal Companion|1	COMPANIONLIST:Animal Companion|Companion (Bat (Dire)),Companion (Giant Vulture)																													SOURCEPAGE:p.104

#Alchemical Trapper
Bomb Trap					KEY:Alchemical Trapper ~ Bomb Trap			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Alchemist Class Features.AlchemicalTrapperClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																		DESC:An alchemical trapper can use one of her bombs to make a trap. Setting a bomb trap is a full-round action that provokes attacks of opportunity. A bomb trap fills a single 5-foot square and cannot be placed in the same area as any other trap. The alchemical trapper needs the same materials required for making a bomb. The DCs for Perception checks to notice the trap, Disable Device checks to disable it, and saving throws to avoid it are equal to the DC for the alchemical trapper's bombs. All bomb traps have location triggers and do not reset. The alchemical trapper can use any one discovery that applies to a bomb when making a bomb trap. The bomb trap lasts %1 minutes. If the bomb trap is not disabled or exploded within that time frame, the trap becomes inert. Creating a bomb trap uses one of the alchemical trapper's bombs per day.|10*AlchemistLVL																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.128
Trapfinding					KEY:Alchemical Trapper ~ Trapfinding		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Alchemist Class Features.AlchemicalTrapperClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																					DEFINE:TrapfindingLVL|0										DESC:An alchemical trapper can find and disable traps, as the rogue class feature of the same name.																																																																																																																																																																																																													ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Rogue ~ Trapfinding																																																																																																																																	BONUS:VAR|TrapfindingLVL|AlchemistLVL																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.128

