Patience of Nature			KEY:Ancient Guardian ~ Patience of Nature		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Druid Class Features.AncientGuardianClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																			DESC:An ancient guardian adds Diplomacy, Perform (oratory), and Sense Motive to her list of class skills and gains an insight bonus equal to half her druid level on such checks.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy,Perform (oratory),Sense Motive|DruidLVL/2|TYPE=Insight																																																CSKILL:Diplomacy|Perform (oratory)|Sense Motive																					SOURCEPAGE:p.140
Ancient Ways				KEY:Ancient Guardian ~ Ancient Ways			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Druid Class Features.AncientGuardianClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																			DESC:An ancient guardian increases any climb, fly, or swim speeds she has or gains via her wild shape ability by 10 feet.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.140
Dispel Hostility				KEY:Ancient Guardian ~ Dispel Hostility		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Druid Class Features.AncientGuardianClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																			DESC:An ancient guardian can channel stored spell energy into a spell capable of dispelling hostile thoughts and strong emotions. She can "lose" a prepared spell in order to cast calm emotions. Instead of the normal Will saving throw for that spell, the DC of a calm emotions spell cast with this ability is %1.|10+DruidLVL/2+WIS																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.140
